            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="divine" key="Lord"><name nymRef="#Κύριος"><w lemma="Κύριος"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">Κ</abbr><ex>ύρι</ex><abbr rend="supraline">ε</abbr></expan></w></name></persName> <choice><orig>ο</orig><reg>ὁ</reg></choice> <persName type="divine" key="God"><name nymRef="#Θεός"></name><w lemma="Θεός"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">Θ</abbr><ex>εὸ</ex><abbr rend="supraline">ς</abbr></expan></w></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><w lemma="ἐγώ"><hi rend="ligature">ἡμ</hi><choice><orig>ὼ</orig><reg>ῶ</reg></choice>ν</w>
                    <lb n="3"/><w lemma="σώζω">σ<choice><orig>ὼ</orig><reg>ῶ</reg></choice>σον </w>
                    <lb n="4"/><hi rend="ligature">τ<choice><orig>ο</orig><reg>ὸ</reg></choice></hi>ν <w lemma="λαός">λ<del rend="erasure">α</del>α
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/><choice><orig>ὸ</orig><reg>ό</reg></choice>ν</w> <w lemma="σύ">σου</w> 
                    <lb n="6"/><w><choice><sic>κ<choice><orig>ε</orig><reg>ὲ</reg></choice></sic><corr>καὶ</corr></choice></w> <w lemma="εὐλογῶ"><choice><sic><expan><abbr>ε<choice><orig>ὑ</orig><reg>ὐ</reg></choice>λόγι</abbr><ex>σον</ex></expan></sic><corr>εὐλόγησον</corr></choice></w>
                 </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Lord, our God, save your people and bless (your inheritance).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. In line 4 it seems that the painter modified the incorrect alpha of the first letter of the word λαόν to form the lambda. In line 6 καί and εὐλόγησον are misspelled. Αccents and breathings with errors. The inscription is from the Second Prayer of the antiphon. 
</p>
            </div>
